vote.title: An ordinance providing for the closure and vacation to vehicular traffic of a portion of Cadillac and Chrysler Drives and Mildred, Roberta and Spivey Streets; and portions of four alleys, containing a total of approximately 165,056 square feet of land, located near the intersection of Cedar Crest Boulevard and Morrell Avenue - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
